Voice models directory — downloaded by setup scripts, gitignored.

Models used:
  - Chatterbox: downloaded automatically by setup-chatterbox.sh
  - Piper EN: en_US-lessac-medium.onnx (~60MB) — downloaded by setup-piper.sh
  - Piper RU: ru_RU-irina-medium.onnx (~60MB) — downloaded by setup-piper.sh
  - Whisper: ggml-large-v3.bin (~3GB) — downloaded by setup-whisper-cpp.sh

To re-download all models:
  cd speech-engines/
  ./setup-chatterbox.sh
  ./setup-piper.sh
  ./setup-whisper-cpp.sh
